info.title: Stackdriver Trace
info.description: Send and retrieve trace data from Stackdriver Trace. Data is generated and available by default for all App Engine applications. Data from other applications can be written to Stackdriver Trace for display, reporting, and analysis.

get.description: Returns of a list of traces that match the specified filter conditions

parameters.name: endTime
parameters.description: Start of the time interval (inclusive) during which the trace data wasncollected from the application

parameters.name: filter
parameters.description: An optional filter for the request

parameters.name: orderBy
parameters.description: Field used to sort the returned traces

parameters.name: pageSize
parameters.description: Maximum number of traces to return

parameters.name: pageToken
parameters.description: Token identifying the page of results to return

parameters.name: projectId
parameters.description: ID of the Cloud project where the trace data is stored

parameters.name: startTime
parameters.description: End of the time interval (inclusive) during which the trace data wasncollected from the application

parameters.name: view
parameters.description: Type of data returned for traces in the list

patch.description: Sends new traces to Stackdriver Trace or updates existing traces

parameters.name: projectId
parameters.description: ID of the Cloud project where the trace data is stored

get.description: Gets a single trace by its ID

parameters.name: projectId
parameters.description: ID of the Cloud project where the trace data is stored

parameters.name: traceId
parameters.description: ID of the trace to return
